data.description: LIKE BRAND NEW!! This Home has everything you need to just move right in! Three spacious bedrooms with an added bonus room that could be used as a fourth bedroom, granite countertops, a large fenced yard, beautiful hardwoods and so much more! Enjoy the relaxing low maintenance 15ft swim spa on the back deck.  The home is set in a cul-de-sac with sidewalk access to the ball fields and greenway! Come enjoy a neighborhood setting with low county taxes in a prime, convenient location! Washer/Dryer convey. SELLER to pay $5,000.00 towards buyers closing cost/escrows or prepaids.
